room_title: Escape room "Graveyard Inlet" by Cipher Seeker Room Escape Challenge in New York
room_description: Your group couldn't resist taking a peek at the "Staff Only" room in the secluded part of the lighthouse. Hearing the tour guide's footsteps approaching one of you hurried to close the door, but now it won't open! Find your way out of the lighthouse keeper's quarters before that woman catches you!
